text:
Drop off 4 shopee packages scan 2 package say another 2 scan later. Checked 3 hours but no update in system for ANY of the packages  (dont know whether she scan correct? This day shift lady staff have habit for scanning/retrieving wrong items) However, i have to say the night shift male staff are very nice and always does excellent job. No answer on number registered to google page called 3 times

Follow up 16-Nov: Shop Owner/IC respond via whatsapp and accepted feedback, said to look into it and re-train staff. Change rating as it was a one-off case and other staffs was great nonetheless
